# 序列化实现

只有 **实现了Serializable或者Externalizable接口** 的 **类** 的 **对象** 才能被序列化为字节序列。（不是则会抛出异常） 

首先类实现序列化接口，其次有类的对象

```
import java.io.Serializable;

public class Person implements Serializable {
    public String name;
    public int age;
    private int weight;
}
```



## 序列化实现

创建一个 **对象输出流**，可以包装其他类型目标输出流，比如 **文件输出流**

```
ObjectOutputStream oos = new ObjectOutputStream(new fileOutputStream("ser.bin"));
```

接着通过对象输出流的  **writeObject(obj); **写入对象

```
oos.writeObject(obj);
```

## 反序列化实现

创建一个 **对象输入流** 可以包装其他类型目标输出流，比如 **文件输入流**

```
ObjectInputStream ois = new ObjectInputStream(new FileInputStream(Filname));
```

接着通过对象输入流的**readObject(obj); **读出对象

```
Object obj = ois.readObject();
return obj;
//这里我将序列化反序列化封装为两个方法
Person person = (Person)unserialize("ser.bin");
```



## 代码

Person.java

```java
import java.io.Serializable;
//实现序列化接口，不然报错
public class Person implements Serializable {
    public String name;
    public int age;
    private int weight;

    public Person(){

    }
    public Person(String name,int age,int weight){
        this.name = name;
        this.age = age;
        this.weight = weight;
    }

    @Override
    public String toString() {
        return "Person{" +
                "name='" + name + '\'' +
                ", age=" + age +
                ", weight=" + weight +
                '}';
    }
}
```

Serialize.java

```java
import java.io.FileNotFoundException;
import java.io.FileOutputStream;
import java.io.IOException;
import java.io.ObjectOutputStream;

public class Serialize {
    public static void serialize(Object obj) throws IOException {
        FileOutputStream fos = new FileOutputStream("ser.bin");
        ObjectOutputStream oos = new ObjectOutputStream(fos);
        oos.writeObject(obj);
        oos.close();
    }
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException {
        Person person = new Person("Tom",20,140);
        serialize(person);
    }
}
```

Unserialize.java

```java
import java.io.FileInputStream;
import java.io.FileNotFoundException;
import java.io.IOException;
import java.io.ObjectInputStream;

public class Unserialize {
    public static Object unserialize(String Filname) throws IOException, ClassNotFoundException {
        FileInputStream fis = new FileInputStream(Filname);
        ObjectInputStream ois = new ObjectInputStream(fis);
        Object obj = ois.readObject();
        return obj;
    }
    public static void main(String[] args) throws IOException, ClassNotFoundException {
        Person person = (Person)unserialize("ser.bin");
        System.out.println(person.toString());
    }
}
```



